summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4160 for the improvement of alley in Block 2, York Addition, being the alley between 33rd Avenue South and 34th Avenue South; from Hanford Street to Horton Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 49699, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
